Class ContactEntry.ContactEntryBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.nyu.cs.addressbook.ContactEntry.ContactEntryBuilder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Builder<ContactEntry>
    Enclosing class:
    ContactEntry

    public static class ContactEntry.ContactEntryBuilder
extends Object
implements Builder<ContactEntry>
    Author:
    shenli

    The ContactEntryBuilder class represents building contact entry information.

    ContactEntryBuilder objects are not constant; their values could be changed after they are created. The ContactEntryBuilder object is not thread-safe. To use it concurrently, user must surround each method invocation with external synchronization of the users' choosing.
